Catalan production

cat = data %>%
  filter(Language=="cat")
head(cat)

cat_model_plot= glm(stress ~ dur_period*pc1*syllable + dur_period*pc2*syllable + f0_spectilt*pc1*syllable + f0_spectilt*pc2*syllable + vowel_periph*pc1*syllable + vowel_periph*pc2*syllable,
                         data = cat, family = "binomial")
summary(cat_model_plot)

Spanish production

spa = data %>%
  filter(Language == "spa")
spa_model_plot= glm(stress ~ dur_period*pc1*syllable + dur_period*pc2*syllable + f0_spectilt*pc1*syllable + f0_spectilt*pc2*syllable +
                      vowel_periph*pc1*syllable + vowel_periph*pc2*syllable,
                    data = spa, family = "binomial")
summary(spa_model_plot)

English production - trilinguals only

English production - by language profile

eng_lang = data %>%
  filter(Language == "eng")
eng_lang_model_plot= glm(stress ~ dur_period*lang_profile*syllable + f0_spectilt*lang_profile*syllable +
                      vowel_periph*lang_profile*syllable,
                    data = eng_lang, family = "binomial")
summary(eng_lang_model_plot)
